{
  "meta": {
    "slug": "svc-restaurant-staff-service-emergency-klf0",
    "category": "pro/service/restaurant_staff",
    "source_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kLf0FEpDE6I",
    "mode": "srt"
  },
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "English Together",
      "zh": "一起學英文",
      "ja": "英語を一緒に学ぼう",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "At the restaurant",
      "zh": "在餐廳裡",
      "ja": "レストランで",
      "time": "00:00:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's learn useful conversation by joining Tom and Angela's first date at the restaurant",
      "zh": "讓我們透過湯姆和安琪拉的第一次約會學習實用對話",
      "ja": "トムとアンジェラの初デートに参加して、役立つ会話を学びましょう",
      "time": "00:00:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Tom, are you ready?",
      "zh": "湯姆，你準備好了嗎？",
      "ja": "トム、準備はいい？",
      "time": "00:00:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, but I'm a bit nervous",
      "zh": "準備好了，但我有點緊張",
      "ja": "はい、でもちょっと緊張しています",
      "time": "00:00:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is my first time dining out with a girl",
      "zh": "這是我第一次和女生外出用餐",
      "ja": "女の子と外食するのは初めてです",
      "time": "00:00:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Don't worry, you'll do great",
      "zh": "別擔心，你會表現得很棒的",
      "ja": "心配しないで、うまくいくよ",
      "time": "00:00:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hi Tom",
      "zh": "嗨，湯姆",
      "ja": "こんにちは、トム",
      "time": "00:00:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hi Angela",
      "zh": "嗨，安琪拉",
      "ja": "こんにちは、アンジェラ",
      "time": "00:00:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You look great",
      "zh": "你看起來很棒",
      "ja": "素敵に見えるよ",
      "time": "00:00:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you",
      "zh": "謝謝",
      "ja": "ありがとう",
      "time": "00:00:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's go inside",
      "zh": "我們進去吧",
      "ja": "中に入りましょう",
      "time": "00:00:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good evening, do you have a reservation?",
      "zh": "晚上好，請問有預約嗎？",
      "ja": "こんばんは、ご予約はありますか？",
      "time": "00:00:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, I do",
      "zh": "有的",
      "ja": "はい、あります",
      "time": "00:00:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's under the name Tom Smith",
      "zh": "預約是湯姆·史密斯的名字",
      "ja": "トム・スミスの名前で予約しています",
      "time": "00:00:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Ah yes, I see it here",
      "zh": "啊，有的，我這裡看到了",
      "ja": "ああ、はい、こちらにあります",
      "time": "00:00:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Right this way, please",
      "zh": "請這邊走",
      "ja": "こちらへどうぞ",
      "time": "00:00:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Here are your menus",
      "zh": "這是你們的菜單",
      "ja": "こちらがメニューです",
      "time": "00:01:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Can I get you anything to drink?",
      "zh": "要喝點什麼嗎？",
      "ja": "お飲み物はいかがですか？",
      "time": "00:01:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, I would like a glass of water, please",
      "zh": "我要一杯水，謝謝",
      "ja": "はい、お水を一杯ください",
      "time": "00:01:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Me too",
      "zh": "我也是",
      "ja": "私も同じです",
      "time": "00:01:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Very good",
      "zh": "很好",
      "ja": "かしこまりました",
      "time": "00:01:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "While you are looking over the menu, could I interest you in an appetizer?",
      "zh": "在您看菜單的時候，要不要先來點開胃菜？",
      "ja": "メニューをご覧の間に、前菜はいかがですか？",
      "time": "00:01:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "An appetizer sounds good",
      "zh": "開胃菜聽起來不錯",
      "ja": "前菜はいいですね",
      "time": "00:01:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Where are your appetizers listed?",
      "zh": "開胃菜在哪一頁？",
      "ja": "前菜はどこに載っていますか？",
      "time": "00:01:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "They are listed on the first page of the menu",
      "zh": "在菜單的第一頁",
      "ja": "メニューの最初のページに載っています",
      "time": "00:01:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Tom, what appetizer do you like?",
      "zh": "湯姆，你想吃什麼開胃菜？",
      "ja": "トム、どの前菜が好き？",
      "time": "00:01:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I would like to start with a Caesar salad please",
      "zh": "我想先來一份凱薩沙拉",
      "ja": "シーザーサラダをお願いします",
      "time": "00:01:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And I'll have the tomato soup",
      "zh": "我想要番茄湯",
      "ja": "私はトマトスープにします",
      "time": "00:01:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Excellent choices",
      "zh": "很棒的選擇",
      "ja": "素晴らしい選択です",
      "time": "00:01:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And would you like to hear about our specials tonight?",
      "zh": "想聽聽我們今晚的特餐嗎？",
      "ja": "今夜のスペシャルはいかがですか？",
      "time": "00:01:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes please",
      "zh": "好，請說",
      "ja": "はい、お願いします",
      "time": "00:01:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Our special tonight is a grilled salmon with a side of roasted vegetables",
      "zh": "今晚的特餐是烤鮭魚搭配烤蔬菜",
      "ja": "今夜のスペシャルはグリルサーモンとロースト野菜のセットです",
      "time": "00:02:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's one of our most popular dishes",
      "zh": "這是我們最受歡迎的菜色之一",
      "ja": "当店で人気の料理の一つです",
      "time": "00:02:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That sounds delicious",
      "zh": "聽起來很好吃",
      "ja": "美味しそうですね",
      "time": "00:02:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I think I'll have that",
      "zh": "我想我要點那個",
      "ja": "それにします",
      "time": "00:02:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I think I'll have the steak with a side of mashed potatoes and grilled vegetables",
      "zh": "我想要牛排，配馬鈴薯泥和烤蔬菜",
      "ja": "ステーキにマッシュポテトとグリル野菜を添えてください",
      "time": "00:02:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And how would you like it cooked?",
      "zh": "牛排要幾分熟？",
      "ja": "焼き加減はいかがなさいますか？",
      "time": "00:02:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I would like well done",
      "zh": "我要全熟",
      "ja": "ウェルダンでお願いします",
      "time": "00:02:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Perfect",
      "zh": "好的",
      "ja": "かしこまりました",
      "time": "00:02:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Your food will be out shortly",
      "zh": "餐點很快就會送上",
      "ja": "お料理はすぐにお持ちします",
      "time": "00:02:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Is there anything else I can get for you in the meantime?",
      "zh": "還需要其他東西嗎？",
      "ja": "他に何かご用意しましょうか？",
      "time": "00:02:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No, that's all",
      "zh": "沒有了，謝謝",
      "ja": "いいえ、それだけです",
      "time": "00:02:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you",
      "zh": "謝謝",
      "ja": "ありがとうございます",
      "time": "00:02:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You're welcome",
      "zh": "不客氣",
      "ja": "どういたしまして",
      "time": "00:02:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Enjoy your meal",
      "zh": "祝您用餐愉快",
      "ja": "ごゆっくりどうぞ",
      "time": "00:02:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What is your favorite dish?",
      "zh": "你最喜歡的菜是什麼？",
      "ja": "あなたの好きな料理は何ですか？",
      "time": "00:02:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Comment below",
      "zh": "請在下方留言",
      "ja": "コメント欄にどうぞ",
      "time": "00:02:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, what should I do now?",
      "zh": "喔，我現在該怎麼辦？",
      "ja": "ああ、今何をすればいい？",
      "time": "00:02:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Tom, chat with Angela",
      "zh": "湯姆，跟安琪拉聊聊吧",
      "ja": "トム、アンジェラと話してみて",
      "time": "00:03:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Why don't you get to know each other better?",
      "zh": "多了解彼此吧",
      "ja": "もっとお互いを知りましょう",
      "time": "00:03:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay",
      "zh": "好",
      "ja": "はい",
      "time": "00:03:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So, Angela",
      "zh": "那麼，安琪拉",
      "ja": "それで、アンジェラ",
      "time": "00:03:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What do you like to do for fun?",
      "zh": "你喜歡做什麼休閒活動？",
      "ja": "趣味は何ですか？",
      "time": "00:03:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Well, I love to travel and explore new places",
      "zh": "我喜歡旅行和探索新地方",
      "ja": "旅行して新しい場所を探検するのが好きです",
      "time": "00:03:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I also enjoy trying new foods",
      "zh": "我也喜歡嘗試新食物",
      "ja": "新しい食べ物を試すのも好きです",
      "time": "00:03:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That's awesome",
      "zh": "太棒了",
      "ja": "素晴らしいですね",
      "time": "00:03:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How about you, Tom?",
      "zh": "你呢，湯姆？",
      "ja": "トムはどう？",
      "time": "00:03:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What do you like to do in your free time?",
      "zh": "你空閒時喜歡做什麼？",
      "ja": "暇な時は何をするのが好きですか？",
      "time": "00:03:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm a big fan of video games and technology",
      "zh": "我很喜歡電玩和科技",
      "ja": "ビデオゲームとテクノロジーが大好きです",
      "time": "00:03:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That's cool",
      "zh": "很酷",
      "ja": "かっこいいね",
      "time": "00:03:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I've never played that game before",
      "zh": "我以前沒玩過那款遊戲",
      "ja": "そのゲームはやったことがありません",
      "time": "00:03:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe you can teach me some time",
      "zh": "也許你可以教我玩",
      "ja": "いつか教えてくれる？",
      "time": "00:03:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah, definitely",
      "zh": "當然可以",
      "ja": "もちろんです",
      "time": "00:03:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, something doesn't seem right with my steak",
      "zh": "喔，我的牛排好像有問題",
      "ja": "あれ、ステーキがおかしいみたい",
      "time": "00:03:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's a bit undercooked",
      "zh": "有點沒熟",
      "ja": "少し焼きが足りません",
      "time": "00:03:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh no, what's wrong with it?",
      "zh": "喔不，怎麼了？",
      "ja": "えっ、どうしたの？",
      "time": "00:03:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's still really pink in the middle and I ordered it well done",
      "zh": "中間還是很粉紅，我點的是全熟",
      "ja": "中がまだピンクで、ウェルダンで頼んだのに",
      "time": "00:04:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Tom, as a gentleman, let's help Angela to tell the waiter",
      "zh": "湯姆，作為紳士，幫安琪拉告訴服務生吧",
      "ja": "トム、紳士としてアンジェラのためにウェイターに伝えましょう",
      "time": "00:04:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That's not good",
      "zh": "這樣不好",
      "ja": "それはよくないね",
      "time": "00:04:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let me tell the waiter",
      "zh": "我來告訴服務生",
      "ja": "私がウェイターに言います",
      "time": "00:04:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sir, is everything okay?",
      "zh": "先生，一切還好嗎？",
      "ja": "お客様、何か問題がありますか？",
      "time": "00:04:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Actually, there's something wrong with the steak",
      "zh": "其實牛排有點問題",
      "ja": "実はステーキに問題があります",
      "time": "00:04:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's undercooked",
      "zh": "沒熟",
      "ja": "焼きが足りません",
      "time": "00:04:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm sorry about that",
      "zh": "很抱歉",
      "ja": "申し訳ございません",
      "time": "00:04:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let me take it back to the kitchen and have them cook it a bit more for you",
      "zh": "我去廚房讓他們幫您多煮一會兒",
      "ja": "キッチンに戻して、もう少し焼かせていただきます",
      "time": "00:04:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thanks",
      "zh": "謝謝",
      "ja": "ありがとうございます",
      "time": "00:04:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thanks for helping me speak up about my steak",
      "zh": "謝謝你幫我說出牛排的問題",
      "ja": "ステーキのことを言ってくれてありがとう",
      "time": "00:04:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I never know how to handle situations like that",
      "zh": "我從不知道該怎麼處理這種情況",
      "ja": "こういう時どうしたらいいか分からなかった",
      "time": "00:04:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No problem",
      "zh": "沒問題",
      "ja": "問題ありません",
      "time": "00:04:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Wow, Tom is more gentleman than I think",
      "zh": "哇，湯姆比我想像中還紳士",
      "ja": "わあ、トムは思ったより紳士的だね",
      "time": "00:04:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Here you go, fresh steak",
      "zh": "給您，新鮮的牛排",
      "ja": "お待たせしました、新しいステーキです",
      "time": "00:04:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Is there anything else I can do for you?",
      "zh": "還需要其他服務嗎？",
      "ja": "他に何かお手伝いできることはありますか？",
      "time": "00:04:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No, that's all",
      "zh": "沒有了",
      "ja": "いいえ、それだけです",
      "time": "00:04:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you for fixing the problem",
      "zh": "謝謝你解決問題",
      "ja": "問題を解決してくれてありがとう",
      "time": "00:05:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You're welcome",
      "zh": "不客氣",
      "ja": "どういたしまして",
      "time": "00:05:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Enjoy your meal",
      "zh": "祝您用餐愉快",
      "ja": "ごゆっくりどうぞ",
      "time": "00:05:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Don't forget to like and subscribe",
      "zh": "別忘了按讚和訂閱",
      "ja": "いいねとチャンネル登録を忘れずに",
      "time": "00:05:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Seems there are two people watching them from a distance",
      "zh": "好像有兩個人在遠處看著他們",
      "ja": "遠くから二人が見ているようです",
      "time": "00:05:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wait, they are Tom's friends",
      "zh": "等等，他們是湯姆的朋友",
      "ja": "あれ、トムの友達だ",
      "time": "00:05:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Jack into Michelle, what are you doing here?",
      "zh": "傑克，蜜雪兒，你們在這裡做什麼？",
      "ja": "ジャック、ミシェル、ここで何してるの？",
      "time": "00:05:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Jack, maybe we should go",
      "zh": "傑克，我們還是走吧",
      "ja": "ジャック、そろそろ行こう",
      "time": "00:05:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Michelle, we are Tom's best friends",
      "zh": "蜜雪兒，我們是湯姆最好的朋友",
      "ja": "ミシェル、僕たちはトムの親友だよ",
      "time": "00:05:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am worried about him",
      "zh": "我很擔心他",
      "ja": "彼のことを心配しているんだ",
      "time": "00:05:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I understand",
      "zh": "我懂",
      "ja": "わかるよ",
      "time": "00:05:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But Tom seems to be doing just fine",
      "zh": "但湯姆看起來過得很好",
      "ja": "でもトムは元気そうだね",
      "time": "00:05:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yeah, he seems to be really enjoying himself",
      "zh": "是啊，他看起來玩得很開心",
      "ja": "うん、すごく楽しんでいるみたい",
      "time": "00:05:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I guess we were worried for nothing",
      "zh": "看來我們多慮了",
      "ja": "心配しすぎたみたいだね",
      "time": "00:05:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm just glad he's happy",
      "zh": "我很高興他快樂",
      "ja": "彼が幸せでよかった",
      "time": "00:05:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "He's been through a lot lately",
      "zh": "他最近經歷了很多",
      "ja": "彼は最近いろいろあったからね",
      "time": "00:05:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Here's your bill",
      "zh": "這是您的帳單",
      "ja": "お会計です",
      "time": "00:05:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Please take your time",
      "zh": "請慢用",
      "ja": "ごゆっくりどうぞ",
      "time": "00:06:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thanks",
      "zh": "謝謝",
      "ja": "ありがとう",
      "time": "00:06:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's see how much we owe",
      "zh": "看看我們欠多少錢",
      "ja": "いくらかかるかな",
      "time": "00:06:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How much do I owe you, Tom?",
      "zh": "湯姆，我欠你多少？",
      "ja": "トム、いくら払えばいい？",
      "time": "00:06:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Don't worry about it",
      "zh": "別擔心",
      "ja": "気にしないで",
      "time": "00:06:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'll take care of it",
      "zh": "我來付",
      "ja": "私が払います",
      "time": "00:06:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Are you sure?",
      "zh": "你確定嗎？",
      "ja": "本当？",
      "time": "00:06:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I don't want to be a burden",
      "zh": "我不想成為負擔",
      "ja": "迷惑かけたくない",
      "time": "00:06:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's my treat",
      "zh": "這次我請客",
      "ja": "今回は私のおごりです",
      "time": "00:06:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You can get the next one",
      "zh": "下次你請",
      "ja": "次はあなたが払ってね",
      "time": "00:06:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay, thank you so much",
      "zh": "好，非常感謝",
      "ja": "わかった、ありがとう",
      "time": "00:06:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That's really kind of you",
      "zh": "你真好",
      "ja": "優しいね",
      "time": "00:06:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Excuse me, sir",
      "zh": "不好意思，先生",
      "ja": "すみません、旦那様",
      "time": "00:06:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can we pay with this card?",
      "zh": "我們可以用這張卡付款嗎？",
      "ja": "このカードで支払えますか？",
      "time": "00:06:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Of course, no problem",
      "zh": "當然可以，沒問題",
      "ja": "もちろん、問題ありません",
      "time": "00:06:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you",
      "zh": "謝謝",
      "ja": "ありがとうございます",
      "time": "00:06:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Have a great evening",
      "zh": "祝您晚上愉快",
      "ja": "良い夜をお過ごしください",
      "time": "00:06:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh my God",
      "zh": "天啊",
      "ja": "なんてこった",
      "time": "00:06:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Tom did very well tonight",
      "zh": "湯姆今晚表現得很好",
      "ja": "トムは今夜とてもよくやったね",
      "time": "00:06:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey Jack, we have to leave before Tom found us",
      "zh": "傑克，我們得在湯姆發現我們前離開",
      "ja": "ジャック、トムに見つかる前に行かないと",
      "time": "00:06:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thanks again, Tom",
      "zh": "再次謝謝你，湯姆",
      "ja": "改めてありがとう、トム",
      "time": "00:07:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I had a great time",
      "zh": "我玩得很開心",
      "ja": "楽しかったです",
      "time": "00:07:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Me too",
      "zh": "我也是",
      "ja": "私もです",
      "time": "00:07:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And the food is so delicious",
      "zh": "食物也非常美味",
      "ja": "料理もとても美味しかった",
      "time": "00:07:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We should come again",
      "zh": "我們應該再來",
      "ja": "また来ましょう",
      "time": "00:07:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Definitely",
      "zh": "一定會",
      "ja": "絶対に",
      "time": "00:07:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Um, do you want to go for a walk?",
      "zh": "嗯，你想去散步嗎？",
      "ja": "えっと、散歩に行きたい？",
      "time": "00:07:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sure",
      "zh": "好啊",
      "ja": "いいよ",
      "time": "00:07:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well done Tom",
      "zh": "做得好，湯姆",
      "ja": "よくやったね、トム",
      "time": "00:07:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You did very well tonight",
      "zh": "你今晚表現得很棒",
      "ja": "今夜はとてもよくできました",
      "time": "00:07:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And thanks for watching",
      "zh": "謝謝收看",
      "ja": "ご視聴ありがとうございました",
      "time": "00:07:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "See you next time",
      "zh": "下次見",
      "ja": "また次回お会いしましょう",
      "time": "00:07:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Thank you",
      "zh": "謝謝",
      "ja": "ありがとうございます",
      "time": "00:08:00"
    }
  ]
}